{"tid":1226401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］請教下請菲傭既事宜","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:55:10.000Z","uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37f925183a90abfd1eb32efa4008c552bf2a904f","tid":1226401,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"第一次請工人姐姐，有家人既同事介紹下，已經揀好咗，菲傭姐姐仲喺菲律賓，未嚟過香港<br />\n<br />\n問咗唔同朋友有唔同講法，想再verify 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問:<br />\n1. 係咪一定要經agent 公司請？如果唔經agent 公司請，咁有咩要注意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 呢個真係想求證下，有人介紹agent 公司俾我，嗰間 agent公司話一定要喺菲律賓training完先過得嚟香港做野，聽落好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />training我喺屋企train佢唔得咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後最後，聽日大家616要上街呀，口號係: <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>暫你老母</strong></span></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d6e1bdd2a7c9f03463c293b695bdf5f887cd2d","tid":1226401,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0255466c7ddfe29f5f96c50412bfd905194167d3","tid":1226401,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d850a92041fd438eae2ab6a5237f30b1fc0eaf9","tid":1226401,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco